data.title: Syrian Lawmakers Eye Retaliatory Sanctions Against United States
data.meta_description: DAMASCUS - More Than 130 Syrian Lawmakers Have Prepared a Draft Law to Impose Sanctions on U.S. Interests in Syria, Parliamentary Sources Said Yesterday.
